12 as deliberation may only occur at a public meeting of the governing body.
13 (g) An informal meeting that includes deliberation or that is for the
14 purpose of exercising a responsibility, authority, power, or duty of a
15 governing body is strictly prohibited.
16 (h) Two (2) or more employees or agents of a public entity may
